g4p_controls

Enum GAlign

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GAlign>
      • g4p_controls.GAlign
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GAlign>

    public enum GAlign
extends java.lang.Enum<GAlign>
    This class provides an enumeration that is used to control the alignment of text and images.
    It also defines the constants for the position of the icon relative to the text.
    Author:
    Peter Lager
